ygData.msgSnippet: There s a slight diffrence in discussing my peepee is larger than your dads than to discuss the pros and cons with a class. If a class is more or less useless
ygData.messageBody:
There's a slight diffrence in discussing my peepee is larger than your dads than to discuss the pros and cons with a class. If a class is more or less useless during raids (IE, what EQ is all about in one way or another) it should be discussed as much as possible so VI notice they gotta do something.
 
And to be honest, i belive there's alot more talk about "My class sux VI, fix it" than the two_year_old_length_comparing talk.
